### Create a space

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/spaces" \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "my-space",
    "relationships": {
      "organization": {
        "data": {
          "guid": "[org-guid]"
        }
      }
    }
  }'

```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :space %>
```

#### Definition
`POST /v3/spaces`

#### Required parameters

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
**name** | _string_ | Space name |
**relationships.organization** | [_to-one relationship_](#to-one-relationships) | A relationship to an organization

#### Optional parameters

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
**metadata.labels** | [_label object_](#labels) | Labels applied to the space
**metadata.annotations** | [_annotation object_](#annotations) | Annotations applied to the space

